<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>oTTo Test Site - Test Pages Home</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css">
  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
</head>

<body>
  <header class="header sticky sticky--top js-header">
    <%- include("../../partials/header-test-pages") %>
  </header>

  <main>


    <div class="container">
      <div data_test_automation_id="Welcome_test_home_text">
        <h1>Welcome to the test pages home area</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="body-wide" data_test_automation_id="about_what_is_this_text" <p>
        <br>
        This is where many of the elements and scenarios are that you will use to test against.
        <br>
        <br>
        Some of the elements may require you to click through to other ares or have designated pages of their own but
        this is the starting point for most of the testing that you may want to do to start with.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <fieldset>
        <div data_test_automation_id="button_click_information_heading">
          <h1>Button click</h1>
        </div>
        <form action="/success-button-click">
          <input data_test_automation_id="generic-button" type="submit" class="ghost-button" value="Click this button"
            href="/success-button-click" title="Verify a button click by clicking this button">
        </form>
      </fieldset>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <fieldset>
        <div data_test_automation_id="button_click_information_heading">
          <h1>Text Entry Field</h1>
        </div>
        <form action="/text-entry-field">
          <input data_test_automation_id="enter-text-entry-field-button" type="submit" class="ghost-button" value="I want to test text entry fields"
            href="/text-entry-field" title="Verify text entry field behaviour by clicking this button">
        </form>
      </fieldset>
    </div>





  </main>

  <footer>
    <%- include("../../partials/footer") %>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>